---
layout: page
title: home
templateEngineOverride: njk, md
---
<article class="flow">
  <section class="flow">
    <h2>Introduction.</h2>
    <p>My name is William. Among other <a
        href="https://williamwhitaker.art">things</a>, I'm
      a front-end developer.</p>
    <div class="flow">
      <h3>Some competencies:</h3>
      <ul role="list" class="cluster">
        <li>HTML</li>
        <li>CSS</li>
        <li>JavaScript</li>
        <li>PHP</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="flow">
    <h2>Thoughtables.</h2>
    <div id="posts">
      {% set postslist = collections.posts %}
      {% include 'partials/postslist.njk' %}
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="flow">
    <aside class="box wide-box">
      <h2>A call to action!</h2>
      <p>Got a project you'd like help with?</p>
      <p>Let's <a
          href="mailto:{{ env.EMAIL_ADDRESS }}">talk</a>!
      </p>
    </aside>
  </section>
</article>
